title: The Supreme Almighty Master (Remake)
summary: The Supreme Almighty Master Remake Manhua The young man, Xia Tian, suddenly obtained x-ray vision and from then on began series of infinite blessings. He was apprenticed to martial arts masters, made friends with treasure experts, and won the favor of countless women… He continued to grow and became the Supreme Almighty Master one step at a time. 新极品全能高手 Xin Jipin Quanneng Gaoshou The Ultimate All-Rounder Remake The Supreme Almighty Master Remake Versatile Martial Arts Ace
